app.long_description:
1. A port of FCE Ultra to the Wii;
2. Use of English as the default UI language;
3. Support multi-language, such as Japanese, German, French, Spanish, Italian, Dutch, Chinese (Simplified and Traditional), Korean, Portuguese, Brazilian Portuguese, Catalan, Turkish, Swedish.

